lead_paragraph: The N.F.L. can do very little to ensure that teams try their best (instead of resting starters) late in the season.
snippet: The N.F.L. can do very little to ensure that teams try their best (instead of resting starters) late in the season. But it discarded what control it did have after Week 16.

headline.main: Did N.F.L. Choose Ratings Over Integrity in Moving Jets-Bengals Game?

abstract: The N.F.L. can do very little to ensure that teams try their best (instead of resting starters) late in the season. But it discarded what control it did have after Week 16.
